Net-SMS-2Way version 0.04
=========================

Hello. Thanks for downloading this module.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  LWP::UserAgent - tested with version 2.031
  HTTP::Request - tested with version 1.40
  Username/Password with http://bulksms.2way.co.za
  Credits with BulkSMS
  
WHAT'S NEW IN v0.04

- Fixed some of the documentation.
- A new and improved version of contrib/send_sms.pl
- Refactored some logic.

GIFTS

 Gifts are gladly accepted.

